Cell["\<\
For given pole parameters Mp and \[CapitalGamma]p, what are the inputs M and \
\[CapitalGamma] for the Sill parametrization?\
\>", "Text",
 CellFrame->{{0, 0}, {0, 0}},
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.974883822455276*^9, 3.9748838559497747`*^9}},
 Background->RGBColor[
